+# Versioned Document Store Implementation Plan
+
+> **For Claude:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use conclave:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task.
+
+**Goal:** Build an in-memory versioned document store with CRUD, version history, branching, and three-way structural merging for JSON documents.
+
+**Architecture:** Four source files — `types.ts` (interfaces), `merge.ts` (three-way merge algorithm), `store.ts` (DocumentStore class), `index.ts` (re-exports). Tests go in `src/__tests__/`. Each branch holds its own document map plus a fork-base snapshot for merge ancestry.
+
+**Tech Stack:** TypeScript 5.4, Node16 modules, vitest for testing, eslint for linting.
+
+---
